---
title: Middle Eastern-Style Beef & Feta Meatballs with Roasted Veggie Couscous
description: The flavours of the Middle East are always a winner, and our tasty veggie couscous and lemony yoghurt dressing are a case in point. Add beef and feta meatballs to the mix and you’ll be hard-pressed to stop your mouth watering while you cook!
image: https://img.hellofresh.com/f_auto,fl_lossy,h_640,q_auto,w_1200/hellofresh_s3/image/middle-eastern-style-beef-feta-meatballs-06198221.jpg
pdf: https://www.hellofresh.co.nz/recipecards/card/middle-eastern-style-beef-feta-meatballs-5ee2e20278211152ce147d6b-7387fed8.pdf
